The following official AWS documentation and white papers. 
These sources provide in-depth information about each component involved in your architecture:

1.	Application Server Interaction with S3:
Amazon S3 Documentation: This documentation covers how applications can interact with S3 for storing and retrieving data.
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/AmazonS3/latest/dev/Introduction.html

Using AWS S3 with EC2: A knowledge article that explains how to use Amazon S3 in conjunction with an EC2 instance (which often acts as the application server).
https://aws.amazon.com/premiumsupport/knowledge-center/ec2-upload-files-to-s3-bucket/

2.	AWS Backup:
AWS Backup Documentation: Provides details on how AWS Backup works, including policies and automated backup processes.
AWS Backup Whitepaper: This whitepaper outlines best practices for using AWS Backup to protect data in the cloud.
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/aws-backup/latest/devguide/whatisbackup.html

3.	Backup Vault in Same Region:
AWS Backup Vaults: This documentation explains how AWS Backup Vaults are used to store backups securely, including region-specific information.
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/aws-backup/latest/devguide/backup-vault.html

4.	Cross-Region/Account Backup Replication:
Cross-Region Backup: An AWS blog post detailing how cross-region backup works within AWS Backup.
https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/aws/aws-backup-now-supports-cross-region-backup/

Cross-Account Backup: Documentation on setting up cross-account backup to enhance disaster recovery strategies.
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/aws-backup/latest/devguide/iam-cross-account-access.html

5.	Amazon SNS for Notifications:
Amazon SNS Documentation: The official documentation on Amazon SNS, covering how to set up notifications for backup events.
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/sns/latest/dg/welcome.html

Using SNS with Backup: Specific information on how to integrate AWS Backup with Amazon SNS for notifications.
https://docs.aws.amazon.com/aws-backup/latest/devguide/monitoring-backup-sns.html

6.	https://aws.amazon.com/devops/

7.	https://www.terraform.io/

8.	https://jenkins.io/

9.	https://github.com/
